19. cscripts
------------
The following scripts have been added:
- csobsinfo: dump information in observation container
- csmodelinfo: dump information in model container
- csmodelmerge: merge model containers into single container
- cstsmapmerge: merge sliced TS map into single map
- csobs2caldb: creates calibration database from observation
- csiactdata: inspects IACT data

The cshessobs script has been renamed to csiactobs.

All GExceptions are replaced by Python RuntimeErrors as the GException
classes are not exposed to Python.


